            <lg xml:id="TK818">
<l>olluṅ karuma muṭaṟṟu pavarkēṇmai</l>
<l>collāṭār cōra viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Gradually abandon without revealing (beforehand) the friendship of those who pretend inability to carry out what they (really) could do.</l>
